data.description: Built on the shores of beautiful Lake Wylie in Clover, SC, a new home at Somerset at Autumn Cove awaits! Eastwood Homes is pleased to be building a variety of innovative and open floor plans in this York County community located mere minutes from Uptown Charlotte, NC and popular Fort Mill, SC. Residents of Autumn Cove enjoy lower taxes and a quiet, calm pace of life plus a community pool, cabana, and boat storage area! Choose from award-winning floor plans including ranch, master-down, two-and-three story options including 1st floor guest suites, 3-car garages, and more. Enjoy large homesites up to ¾ of an acre plus wooded homesite availability.  Visit today to experience the excitement of owning a new home in Somerset at Autumn Cove!
